# VOICES KG v2 — external alignment
#
# 2530 skos:exactMatch triples linking minted urn:voices:place:<slug> IRIs
# to external authority files (GeoNames, Wikidata). The SFI thesaurus
# content is not included anywhere in this repository — only the place
# names extracted from event mentions are re-minted as local IRIs and
# aligned outward via SKOS, the same way GeoNames and Wikidata themselves
# express cross-vocabulary references.
#
# Regenerate via:
#   curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3032/voices/sparql \
#     --data-urlencode "query=CONSTRUCT { ?s ?p ?o } WHERE { GRAPH <urn:voices:graph:alignment> { ?s ?p ?o } }" \
#     -H "Accept: text/turtle" > schema/voices-alignment-v2.ttl
#
@prefix skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> .

